title: Bug 121170 - getcolumnlabel from meta data object does not return recognizable strings
description: The labels returned before extraction are null, while the ones after extraction are recognizable strings.
OB: The labels returned before extraction are null.
EB: getcolumnlabel before extraction should also return the same labels as after extraction.
SR:
1. Initialize the meta data object.
2. Call getcolumnlabel on the meta data object before extracting any data.
3. Verify that the labels returned are the same as the labels returned after extraction.
